lenders.name: Maintain Plumbing
lenders.occupational_info:
Plumbing on the Gold Coast. We deliver plumbing of all types from small domestic jobs to large commercial. 

The Maintain Plumbing team has extensive experience in all facets of plumbing maintenance. 

Like all other industries the plumbing industry has seen many changes over the years. 

With over 30 years of experience there is not much that we have not seen or fixed in our time.

From the days of septic tanks to the latest solar hot water systems we have seen it all. We have gone from lead pipes to galvanised steel pipes to copper pipes to plastic pipes. We have gone from plungers to hand rods to eclectic eels to jet blasting drain cleaners.

At maintain plumbing we have tackled these changes by always keeping up with the latest technology and equipment. We have invested in the most modern drain cleaning jet blasters available. We have the latest in all other plumbing maintenance tools and equipment. 

Contact address: 5b/90 Bundall Road, Gold Coast, QLD 4217, phone - 1800236826
